\begin_layout Enumerate
The inclusion 
\begin_inset Formula $IJ\subset I\cap J$
\end_inset

 holds in every ring.
 For the reverse inclusion, we have 
\begin_inset Formula $I\cap J=(I\cap J)(I+J)\subseteq IJ$
\end_inset

.
