 (The Chinese Remainder Theorem) Let 
\begin_inset Formula $I_{1},\dots,I_{k}$
\end_inset

 be pairwise relatively prime ideals in 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

.
 Then 
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
R\slash I_{1}\cdots I_{k}\cong R\slash I_{1}\times\cdots\times R\slash I_{k}.
\]

\end_inset


\begin_inset ERT
status open

\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
end{theorem}
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

